GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 10th March, 2018
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 10th March, 2018:
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Civil Aviation;
and
i)
ii)
Shri Suresh Prabhu assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Civil Aviation. He
will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Commerce and Industry.
